channel.title: Looking to be a 728 Coder
channel.description:
Hello guys, this is probarably the wrong section? Yes but i'm not good with forums and stuff. I'm basicly bored, i have alot of free time and i'm looking for a server that is 718-728 and is in need of a coder. I am [u]NOT[/u] a 'Java Programmer' and i am [u]NOT[/u] a brilliant coder.

Please, like seriously, don't flame or hate - I simply can't be arsed having arguments with people i don't know. Don't judge? I'm not saying i'm a brilliant coder, but i can make a server worth playing.
Timezone: Whatever a UK timezone is called.
Skype: Simpleservers2012
Much love.
